                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Increases the cursor speed on the battle screen -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>				  
                  <br>&nbsp; Returns to the previous screen during menu commands / Cancel action in battle -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>				  
                  <br>&nbsp; Displays units screen -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad Up + Square Button</font>				  
                  <br>&nbsp; Displays system menu -
