                  <br>&nbsp; Displays map screen -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad Down + Square Button</font>						  
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn on/off battle animations -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
